<h2>About BookMeUp</h2>
<ul>
<li>"BookMeUp" uses the <a class="amazon" href="https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/gp/advertising/api/detail/main.html">Amazon Product Advertising API</a> to suggest related books to read based on a user's location and/or search query.</li>
<li>This app is built with php, javascript, and html and optimized for mobile environments. Other APIs used for data sources include: MapFast from OCLC, the Worldcat Search API, and the Open Library Cover Image API.</li>
</ul>